{"questionId":"22446950","questionHtml":"<p>Write down an expression for the amount charged to deliver a package of weight <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo> </mo><mi>kg</mi></math>, where <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>5</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>OR&nbsp; &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>5</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em>A1A1</em></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for a linear expression with a gradient of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn></math>,<br><em><strong>A1</strong></em> for a completely correct expression in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22446950","referenceCode":"24M.2.AHL.TZ1.1e","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Write down an expression for the amount charged to deliver a package of weight x kg, where x>1.","paper":"2","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"e","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.5—Modelling functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.6—Modelling skills"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}